Package: GoBayes
Title: Bayesian Go/No-Go Operating Characteristic Calculations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("GoBayes", "Chen Chao", , "chenchaostat@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight client package for Bayesian Go/No-Go operating 
    characteristic calculations. Core computations are executed on a remote 
    GoBayes API server, while the R package provides user-facing functions, 
    API configuration, result formatting, and printing methods.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/chenchaostat/GoBayes
BugReports: https://github.com/chenchaostat/GoBayes/issues
